{"tid":2085500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［七一遊行］好想趁呢個機會多謝大家","createTime":"2020-06-30T02:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T04:36:41.000Z","uid":190296,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"760f4ddd0971d0f3242218749f26c77f7840508a","tid":2085500,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"係整整一年嘅時間裏面 <br />\n我哋經歷咗好多好唔開心嘅事<br />\n難免會傷心 失望 甚至有啲不知所措<br />\n但同大家就變到好似朋友一樣 <br />\n即使我哋每一個都素未謀面<br />\n我哋會係網上一齊互相分享情緒 <br />\n<br />\n好想多謝每一位仍然堅持緊嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算之前面對有幾多分化 有幾多唔好聽嘅說話<br />\n我哋依家係時候集合一齊 只要立場相同 <br />\n無論付出多定少 我哋都係同路人<br />\n聽日一齊去向國際證明 我哋香港人<br />\n即使面對極權依然會繼續堅守我哋嘅信念<br />\n<br />\n一齊早啲瞓 聽日出黎見證真。香港人精神<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">七月一日 明天見</span></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8RVMuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8RVMuF.jpg&h=af3b35fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raUL8H0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraUL8H0.jpg&h=6ef35671&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVKTx9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVKTx9G.jpg&h=e825344e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">能夠成為香港人<br />\n係我一生人嘅驕傲</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338643242f6b91518f7f77b814ada525346e1fcf","tid":2085500,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbQCZSu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbQCZSu.jpg&h=581ee4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins> 兩點鐘 維園見</ins></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a7ab940fda113f8f39aa0984c19cee3300648237","tid":2085500,"uid":190296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVGOm6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVGOm6N.jpg&h=fff9d3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrVfMyt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrVfMyt.jpg&h=68e1951e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1CFddt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1CFddt.jpg&h=c42d69d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21b74ab66cfc464286bc5a3a6d101c86d3b709cc","tid":2085500,"uid":190221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa018b99b6e61c58ca42f49dca7889ea54c7517","tid":2085500,"uid":145362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:12:31.000Z","msg":"我愛手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"0b36f16ec727fbb21fc3afd6cafa1bd18d156f40","tid":2085500,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=